title: JanSport Pack Review: Hawk Ridge
description: Hit the road, trail or path with the JanSport Hawk Ridge backpack, featuring a laptop or hydration system pocket, large zippered stash pocket, front organizer pocket and twin water bottle pockets.

transcripts: Hey guys I'm Ahren back designer here at jansport and today I'm going to walk you through some awesome new product we're going to talk about the hawk ridge today part of her outside collection this is a 26 liter pack made out of 600 denier polyester and features synthetic leather touch points and trims first thing we'll do is take a look at the back we got s-curve padded shoulder straps and nicely padded back panel you'll also notice a hydration port here where the laptop sleeve serves to hold up to a three liter water bladder on the side here you've got real quick and easy access to the laptop sleeve is dedicated and fully padded and it's a 15 inch laptop main compartment nice big open space sir for your 26 liters you got dual water bottle pockets on the sides up top is a quick stash pocket it's got a good bit of depth just a great place to throw things you got your cables here nice little organizer this is also where your carabiner key clip lives in the front so nice vertical stash pocket is also a nice bit of depth in here but it's a great spot to throw no books and journals and as a daisy chain down the front with a nice gear loop and a lashing square to finish it off and that is your hawk ridge as always guaranteed for life.
